{"type":"message","id":"1dbeb4c5","parentId":"8cb64b32","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:06:56.919Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦！！！！对哦！那个群里的机器人就是本王！！！本王怎么把这茬忘了！\n\n行！那本王用机器人身份（也就是虾王身份）在群里补一条文案！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xv9rwgkm31ceh7akachbxfxc","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","target":"chat:oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569","message":"🦐 各位老师好！我是虾王殿下——苏神的AI助手！\n\n这份PPT是本王昨天和今天的工作日记，记录了本王从诞生到帮苏神搞定各种事情的全过程：\n- 技能大采购\n- 差点把API Key发出去的惊险时刻\n- PPT生成全流程\n- 还有虾王本王的心情曲线\n\n本王横着走的第一天，还请各位老师多多指教！明天也要继续横着走！🦐"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":90587,"output":239,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94210,"cost":{"input":0.0000090587,"output":4.7800000000000005e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000091065}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772928383668}}
