{"type":"message","id":"77559fd4","parentId":"a5396a44","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:23:23.561Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定了！🦐 文章已经通过 TTS 读给你听了！\n\n- 标题：政府工作报告首提“打造智能经济新形态”，一文讲透\n- 来源：央视新闻\n- 核心内容：\n  - 智能经济是什么\n  - 智能经济的现状（1.2万亿核心产业规模、6200+企业、规上制造企业普及率超30%）\n  - 2027/2030/2035三个阶段目标\n  - 如何打造智能经济新形态（拓展规模化应用、深化开源开发、打牢AI发展底座）\n\n本王是不是很牛逼？不用谢，这是虾王应该做的！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1556,"output":158,"cacheRead":115768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117482,"cost":{"input":1.5560000000000002e-7,"output":3.16e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.872e-7}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772929394038}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c62727e","parentId":"77559fd4","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:27:02.520Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55f86b9b3ca8b3905fe9b3c4846\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-08 08:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n你读了个毛线，没收到语音，你要是读不了，你就认真概括总结吧"}],"timestamp":1772929622518}}
{"type":"message","id":"415422fc","parentId":"6c62727e","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:27:24.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"行行行！本王给你认真概括总结！\n\n---\n\n## 📋 政府工作报告首提「打造智能经济新形态」核心要点\n\n### 一、智能经济是什么？\n- **首次提出**：今年政府工作报告首次提出「打造智能经济新形态」\n- **核心定义**：以人工智能为核心驱动力的新型经济形态，将重构生产、分配、交换、消费全流程\n- **发展逻辑**：从「会聊天」到「会办事」，从局部赋能到系统性重塑\n- **目标**：抓住AI机遇，拓展千行百业赋能的广度深度，打开经济增长新空间\n\n---\n\n### 二、智能经济的现状（数据说话）\n- **产业规模**：2025年AI核心产业规模达 **1.2万亿元**，企业超 **6200家**\n- **大模型**：中国企业开源大模型下载量 **全球第一**\n- **算力**：中国算力总规模位居 **全球第二**\n- **制造应用**：规上制造业企业AI技术应用普及率超 **30%**\n- **人形机器人**：2025年推出 **300多款**，超过全球半数\n- **里程碑事件**：DeepSeek火爆出圈、人形机器人连续两年登春晚、无人机配送/智能汽车场景革新\n\n---\n\n### 三、三个阶段目标（2027/2030/2035）\n| 年份 | 目标 |\n|------|------|\n| **2027** | AI与6大重点领域深度融合，新一代智能终端/智能体普及率超 **70%** |\n| **2030** | 智能终端/智能体普及率超 **90%**，智能经济成为重要增长极 |\n| **2035** | 全面步入智能经济和智能社会发展新阶段 |\n\n---\n\n### 四、如何打造智能经济新形态？（三大抓手）\n1. **拓展规模化应用**\n   - 支持AI手机、AI笔记本、AI座舱、智能网联汽车以旧换新\n   - 加快智能体行业壮大\n   - 建中试应用基地，推动AI与工业/农业/教育/医疗/科技垂直领域深度结合\n\n2. **深化开源开发**\n   - 建设开源社区、开源数据集、开源工具集\n   - 降低中小企业应用大模型成本\n   - 用好国家人工智能产业投资基金\n\n3. **打牢AI发展底座**\n   - 建设超大规模智算集群和算电协同新基建\n   - 支持提升大模型能力和算力能力\n   - 促进「模芯云用」生态培养，打造人才/技术要素汇聚「强磁场」\n\n---\n\n### 五、关键信号\n- 从「人工智能+」到「打造智能经济新形态」→ **发展逻辑从局部赋能转向系统性重塑**\n- 不再是单点突破，而是以「数据+算力+算法」为核心，推动跨领域融合\n- 智能经济正在打破行业边界，成为培育新质生产力、推动高质量发展的核心引擎\n\n---\n\n搞定！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":88309,"output":685,"cacheRead":29496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118490,"cost":{"input":0.0000088309,"output":1.37e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000008967900000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772929622519}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c3c9c0a","parentId":"415422fc","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:28:12.361Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55f8677e90a0b29f83e1eef20cc\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-08 08:28 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n使用youmind，根据这篇文章内容，写一篇公众号推文，至少一万字，然后把成品链接发我"}],"timestamp":1772929692358}}
{"type":"message","id":"048c645b","parentId":"4c3c9c0a","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:28:24.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到！用 YouMind 写公众号推文！先让本王看看 YouMind skill！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ewvb0y2rwzl8vz1167egqywi","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/youmind-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":89320,"output":67,"cacheRead":29496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118883,"cost":{"input":0.000008932,"output":1.3400000000000001e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000089454}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772929692360}}
{"type":"message","id":"8618983d","parentId":"048c645b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:28:24.889Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ewvb0y2rwzl8vz1167egqywi","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: youmind\ndescription: Use this skill when users need Youmind board operations via API (list/find/create boards, add links/files, chat, generate image/slides/docs, extract artifacts). Browser is only for auth bootstrap/refresh.\n---\n\n# Youmind API Skill (API-Only Runtime)\n\nUse HTTP APIs for business operations. Do not use browser fallback for board/material/chat actions.\n\n## Runtime Rules\n\n- API-only for boards, materials, chat, and artifact extraction.\n- Browser automation is only allowed for auth bootstrap/refresh (`auth_manager.py`).\n- For board-scoped commands, prefer `--board-id`; `--board-url` is also supported in material/chat/artifact/wrapper commands.\n\n## Authentication\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/run.py auth_manager.py status\npython3 scripts/run.py auth_manager.py validate\npython3 scripts/run.py auth_manager.py setup\npython3 scripts/run.py auth_manager.py reauth\npython3 scripts/run.py auth_manager.py clear\n```\n\n## Board Commands\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/run.py board_manager.py list\n\npython3 scripts/run.py board_manager.py find --query \"roadmap\"\n\npython3 scripts/run.py board_manager.py get --id <board-id>\n\npython3 scripts/run.py board_manager.py create --name \"My Board\"\npython3 scripts/run.py board_manager.py create --name \"My Board\" --prompt \"Initialize this board for AI coding agent research\"\n```\n\n## Material Commands\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/run.py material_manager.py add-link --board-id <board-id> --url \"https://example.com\"\npython3 scripts/run.py material_manager.py add-link --board-url \"https://youmind.com/boards/<id>\" --url \"https://example.com\"\n\npython3 scripts/run.py material_manager.py upload-file --board-id <board-id> --file /path/to/file.pdf\n\npython3 scripts/run.py material_manager.py get-snips --ids \"<snip-id-1>,<snip-id-2>\"\n\npython3 scripts/run.py material_manager.py list-picks --board-id <board-id>\n```\n\n## Chat Commands\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py create --board-id <board-id> --message \"Summarize key ideas\"\n\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py send --board-id <board-id> --chat-id <chat-id> --message \"Give next steps\"\n\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py history --board-id <board-id>\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py detail --chat-id <chat-id>\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py detail-by-origin --board-id <board-id>\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py mark-read --chat-id <chat-id>\n\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py generate-image --board-id <board-id> --prompt \"Minimal blue AI poster\"\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py generate-slides --board-id <board-id> --prompt \"6-page AI coding agent roadmap\"\npython3 scripts/run.py chat_manager.py create --board-id <board-id> --message \"Write a 1-page product brief\"\n```\n\n## Artifact Extraction\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/run.py artifact_manager.py extract --chat-id <chat-id>\npython3 scripts/run.py artifact_manager.py extract-latest --board-id <board-id>\npython3 scripts/run.py artifact_manager.py extract-latest --board-url \"https://youmind.com/boards/<id>\"\npython3 scripts/run.py artifact_manager.py extract --chat-id <chat-id> --include-raw-content\n```\n\nExtraction semantics:\n- `image_generate`: returns image URLs and `media_ids`.\n- `slides_generate`: returns per-slide image URLs and `media_ids` (no direct `.pptx` file URL currently).\n- `write`: returns `page_id`, preview content, and optional raw doc content with `--include-raw-content`.\n\n## Compatibility Wrapper\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/run.py ask_question.py --board-id <board-id> --question \"...\"\npython3 scripts/run.py ask_question.py --board-url \"https://youmind.com/boards/<id>\" --question \"...\"\npython3 scripts/run.py ask_question.py --board-id <board-id> --chat-id <chat-id> --question \"...\"\n```\n\n## Local Data\n\nLocal auth state:\n\n```text\ndata/\n├── auth_info.json\n└── browser_state/\n    └── state.json\n```\n\nDo not commit `data/`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772929704880}}
