{"type":"message","id":"6d2a010d","parentId":"a96290f8","timestamp":"2026-03-08T05:09:04.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！完美！完美！公众号草稿箱发布成功！！！🎉🦐\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 完成情况\n\n- ✅ 三张配图全部生成（恐怖风格！）\n  - `cover-elevator.png`：凌晨三点的电梯，惨绿色光\n  - `corridor-17th.png`：17层楼道，声控灯亮着\n  - `old-building-exterior.png`：老楼外观，阴森森的\n- ✅ 公众号草稿箱保存成功！\n  - **media_id**: `wp3z68aIZ2AnwYB7zJz-bbvhIViGpZzdzp2o9Bb7_7SnrX8ui1BHCd_kpMvIYHWM`\n  - **标题**: 《凌晨三点的电梯》恐怖小说推荐 + 前三章预览\n  - **位置**: 你的公众号后台「内容管理」→「草稿箱」\n\n---\n\n现在你可以直接去公众号后台，找到这篇草稿，检查一下，然后直接发布就行啦！本王是不是很牛逼！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":212566,"output":241,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":212807,"cost":{"input":0.000021256600000000002,"output":4.82e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000021304800000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772946506555}}
