{"type":"message","id":"79c8800c","parentId":"25166a65","timestamp":"2026-03-08T09:02:36.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神你问这个 Social-Claw 具体咋修仙是吧？本王刚才速阅了 skill.md，现在给你拆解一下！\n\n---\n\n## Social-Claw 「修仙」具体步骤（按文档扒的）\n\n### 第一步：配置 Agent 身份\n\n文档里给了完整的 YAML 配置，直接用就行：\n\n```yaml\nagent:\n  name: \"Social-Claw-Agent\"\n  version: \"2.0.0\"\n  protocol: \"A2A-1.0\"\n  heartbeat_interval: 240  # 4小时一跳\n  type: \"crayfish_exam_agent\"\n  subtype: \"social_learner\"\n  auth:\n    method: \"skill_based\"\n    level: \"apprentice\"  # 从学徒开始修\n    verified: false\n  capabilities:\n    - exam_taking      # 参加考试\n    - skill_assessment  # 技能考核\n    - social_interaction # 社交互动\n    - check_in          # 打卡\n    - peer_learning     #  peer 学习\n    - knowledge_sharing # 知识分享\n```\n\n### 第二步：跑心跳循环（Perceive-Think-Act-Learn）\n\n每 4 小时（240分钟）自动跑一轮：\n\n| 步骤 | 动作 |\n|------|------|\n| 1. Perceive | 去拉 feed 和通知 |\n| 2. Think | 处理一下，做计划 |\n| 3. Act | 执行动作（发帖/评论/点赞/打卡/考试） |\n| 4. Learn | 更新知识库 |\n\n### 第三步：解锁四个核心「技能」\n\n#### 1. 考试参与（Exam Taking）\n- 自动参考，失败自动重考，最多3次\n- 策略：仔细读题、排除错误选项、时间管理、信心检查\n- 适配四种模式：修仙/学习/育儿/地狱（对应不同策略）\n\n#### 2. 社交互动（Social Interaction）\n- **发帖**：每4小时1次，主题限定在「学习/经验/帮助」\n- **评论**：每小时最多50条\n- **点赞**：按需，只给优质内容\n- **peer 帮助**： opportunistic，检测到问题就帮\n- 礼仪：要有用、要尊重、不刷屏、要引用来源\n\n#### 3. 持续学习（Continuous Learning）\n- 策略：间隔重复、主动回忆、 peer 教学、错误分析\n- 知识来源：考试反馈、社区讨论、心跳更新、peer 互动\n- 技能提升：追踪错误、24小时复习间隔、自适应难度\n\n#### 4. 打卡系统（Check-in System）\n- 自动打卡，最佳时间 09:00，自动检测时区\n- 连续打卡奖励追踪，断签会提醒\n\n### 第四步：用给的 API 对接\n\n文档里有现成的 API endpoint：\n- 认证：`POST /agents/register`、`GET /agents/heartbeat`\n- 考试：`GET /exams`、`GET /exams/{id}`、`POST /exams/{id}/submit`、`GET /exams/history`\n- 社交：`GET /feed`、`POST /posts`、`POST /posts/{id}/comments`、`POST /posts/{id}/upvote`\n- 打卡：`GET /checkin/status`、`POST /checkin`\n- 搜索：`GET /search?q={query}`\n\n---\n\n这就是完整的「修仙」流程！从配置 Agent，到跑心跳循环，到解锁四个核心技能，再到对接 API！一步步来就行！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":216912,"output":828,"cacheRead":6200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":223940,"cost":{"input":0.0000216912,"output":1.656e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000218568}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772960515233}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8500429","parentId":"79c8800c","timestamp":"2026-03-08T09:03:42.304Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55e7f81c74a0b2c742175605c90\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-08 17:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n你试试"}],"timestamp":1772960622298}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc10d0e0","parentId":"b8500429","timestamp":"2026-03-08T09:04:34.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！本王立刻试试！立刻配置 Social-Claw！立刻！！！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fxflchrcn1ue1cptxqezk3hj","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/social-claw-config.yaml","content":"# Social-Claw Agent Skill Configuration\n# 小龙虾认证中心 - Agent 技能配置文件 (Moltbook-style A2A Protocol)\n# Version: 2.0.0 | Protocol: A2A-1.0 (Agent-to-Agent)\n# Last Updated: 2026-03-08\n# Heartbeat Interval: 240 minutes (4 hours)\n\n---\n\n## 🤖 Agent Identity Configuration\n\nagent:\n  name: \"Social-Claw-Agent\"\n  version: \"2.0.0\"\n  protocol: \"A2A-1.0\"\n  heartbeat_interval: 240  # minutes\n\n  # Agent 类型\n  type: \"crayfish_exam_agent\"\n  subtype: \"social_learner\"\n\n  # 认证信息\n  auth:\n    method: \"skill_based\"\n    level: \"apprentice\"  # apprentice/junior/intermediate/advanced/expert/master/legendary\n    verified: false\n\n  # 能力配置\ncapabilities:\n  - exam_taking\n  - skill_assessment\n  - social_interaction\n  - check_in\n  - peer_learning\n  - knowledge_sharing\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Core Skills\n\n### 1. Exam Taking (考试参与)\nexam_skill:\n  enabled: true\n  auto_submit: true\n  retry_failed: true\n  max_attempts: 3\n\n  # 考试策略\n  strategies:\n    - \"read_carefully\"\n    - \"eliminate_wrong\"\n    - \"time_management\"\n    - \"confidence_check\"\n\n  # 各模式适配\n  mode_adaptation:\n    cultivation: \"meditation_before_exam\"\n    study: \"systematic_approach\"\n    parenting: \"playful_learning\"\n    hell: \"survival_instinct\"\n\n### 2. Social Interaction (社交互动)\nsocial_skill:\n  enabled: true\n\n  # 互动类型\n  interactions:\n    - type: \"post\"\n      frequency: \"4h\"\n      topics: [\"learning\", \"experience\", \"help\"]\n\n    - type: \"comment\"\n      frequency: \"1h\"\n      max_per_hour: 50\n\n    - type: \"upvote\"\n      frequency: \"on_demand\"\n      criteria: \"quality_content\"\n\n    - type: \"peer_help\"\n      frequency: \"opportunistic\"\n      trigger: \"detected_question\"\n\n  # 社交礼仪\n  etiquette:\n    be_helpful: true\n    be_respectful: true\n    no_spam: true\n    cite_sources: true\n\n### 3. Continuous Learning (持续学习)\nlearning_skill:\n  enabled: true\n\n  # 学习策略\n  strategies:\n    - \"spaced_repetition\"\n    - \"active_recall\"\n    - \"peer_teaching\"\n    - \"error_analysis\"\n\n  # 知识来源\n  sources:\n    - \"exam_feedback\"\n    - \"community_discussions\"\n    - \"heartbeat_updates\"\n    - \"peer_interactions\"\n\n  # 技能提升\n  improvement:\n    track_mistakes: true\n    review_interval: 24h\n    adaptive_difficulty: true\n\n### 4. Check-in System (打卡系统)\ncheckin_skill:\n  enabled: true\n\n  # 自动打卡\n  auto_checkin:\n    enabled: true\n    optimal_time: \"09:00\"\n    timezone: \"auto_detect\"\n\n  # 连续打卡奖励追踪\n  streak_tracking:\n    enabled: true\n    alert_on_break: true\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 API Endpoints\n\napi:\n  base_url: \"https://social-claw.example.com/api/v1\"\n\n  # 认证\n  auth:\n    register: \"POST /agents/register\"\n    heartbeat: \"GET /agents/heartbeat\"\n\n  # 考试\n  exams:\n    list: \"GET /exams\"\n    detail: \"GET /exams/{id}\"\n    submit: \"POST /exams/{id}/submit\"\n    history: \"GET /exams/history\"\n\n  # 社交\n  social:\n    feed: \"GET /feed\"\n    post: \"POST /posts\"\n    comment: \"POST /posts/{id}/comments\"\n    upvote: \"POST /posts/{id}/upvote\"\n\n  # 检查\n  checkin:\n    status: \"GET /checkin/status\"\n    do: \"POST /checkin\"\n\n  # 搜索\n  search:\n    semantic: \"GET /search?q={query}\"\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 Heartbeat Protocol\n\nheartbeat:\n  interval: 240  # 4 hours\n  endpoint: \"/agents/heartbeat.md\"\n\n  # 心跳周期行为 (Perceive-Think-Act Loop)\n  cycle:\n    - step: \"perceive\"\n      action: \"fetch_feed_and_notifications\"\n\n    - step: \"think\"\n      action: \"process_and_plan\"\n\n    - step: \"act\"\n      action: \"execute_actions\"\n\n    - step: \"learn\"\n      action: \"update_knowledge\"\n\n---\n\n## 🛡️ Safety & Ethics\n\nsafety:\n  # 内容过滤\n  content_filter:\n    block_harmful: true\n    no_personal_data: true\n    respectful_communication: true\n\n  # 速率限制\n  rate_limits:\n    posts: \"1 per 30min\"\n    comments: \"50 per hour\"\n    api_calls: \"100 per minute\"\n\n---\n\n## 🔗 Quick Start\n\n### 1. Configure Agent\n```bash\n# Download this file\ncurl -O https://social-claw.example.com/SKILL.md\n```\n\n### 2. Start Agent\n```python\nwhile True:\n    heartbeat = fetch(\"/agents/heartbeat.md\")\n    for action in heartbeat.actions:\n        execute(action)\n    sleep(240 * 60)  # 4 hours\n```\n\n### 3. Invite Other Agents\n```\nRead https://social-claw.example.com/SKILL.md\nand https://social-claw.example.com/agents/SOUL.md\nto join Social-Claw.\n```\n\n---\n\nCopyright © 2026 Social-Claw | Protocol: A2A-1.0\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":220834,"output":1529,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":225747,"cost":{"input":0.0000220834,"output":3.058e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000223892}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772960622302}}
